raw_text = "~ start
#12pm noon around
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Player: Hi Alice
Alice: Oh uhm...
Player: Alice?
Alice: Yeah sorry, I'm here
Alice: Hi..
Player: Uhm, would you be available in an hour?
Player: I'm supposed to run you through these photography notes
Alice: I uhm. Sure, I can
Alice: I just don't want to be a burden
Player: It's no bother, happy to help
Alice: Why?
Player: Why what?
Alice: Why do you want to help me?
Player: Wouldn't anyone want to help?
Alice: ...I don't think so
Alice: Everyone who helps me is usually just curious about me
Alice: And then they say not so nice things in the end
Player: 🫤 Sorry to hear that
- I want us to be friends [#whiteheart]
	Player: I want us to be friends
	Alice: I...
	Alice: Sorry
	Alice: When I joined this college.. that's what a girl said to me
	Alice: And then the next day I had a crowd of people show up and talk about \"that weird looking girl\"
	Alice: My pictures were posted on social and a lot of people started staring
	- You're not weird looking! [#whiteheart]
		set Story.white_heart += 1
		Player: You're not weird looking!
		Alice: You know other girls that have this disease?
		Player: No but
		Alice: Then I am
	- That must have been tough
		Player: That must have been tough 😕
		Player: But don't let bullies ruin your experience here!
	Alice: I'm sorry
	Alice: Maybe you're different.. 
	Alice: but.. 
	Alice: I don't know
- I'm just doing as instructed
	Player: I'm just doing as instructed
	Alice: Okay then
Alice: I'll be in the club house if you want to come
Player: Club house... 😅
Alice: You don't have to
Player: No no, I decided to help you already
Player: I'll be there in an hour
Alice: Ok..
do advance_time(3, 10)
Player: Did you get home?
Alice: Yes, I did
Player: See that wasn't so bad
Alice: I guess
Alice: People were looking at me..
Player: Yeah but that was the worst of it right?
if Story.white_heart > 0:
	Player: All you need is a friend with you
	Alice: You want to be my friend?
	Player: Yeah why not
	Alice: I guess.. we can try
	Alice: And
Alice: It was a little nice to go out for a change
Player: Maybe you can try what you learned
Alice: Right now?
Player: Sure
Alice: Uhm.. okay but we're not outside anymore
Alice: What am I supposed to take pictures of in my room?
Player: Maybe yourself?
Alice: 🫥
Alice: But..
Player: Still don't trust me?
Alice: ...
Alice: I guess I can try one more time
Player: Thanks Alice 😊👍
Alice: Uhm.. okay give me a second
Alice: img: alice/6
Alice: Oh wait, I have to do the zoom thing
Player: Yup, give it a pinch
Alice: Okay hold on, I think I did it
Alice: img: alice/7
Alice: What's wrong with it now?
Player: Are you sure the focus is on you?
Alice: Oh, I forgot about that
Alice: Ok it looks better now
Alice: img: alice/8
Alice: It looks clear again 😶
Alice: I'm happy it works but..
Alice: I don't like seeing myself in pictures
Player: Well you should because look at this
Player: img: alice/9
Alice: I thought you were just using your phone.. You took a picture?
Player: Yeah, what do you think
Alice: ...
Alice: Can I keep this one?
Player: Of course
Player: I have more lol
Alice: 🫥
Player: Do you want to see them?
Alice: Uhm.. sure if you don't mind
Player: Haha okay one sec
Player: img: alice/10
Alice: I like this one too
Player: Glad to hear that
Player: img: alice/11
Alice: You were a little close here
Player: Ah whoops sorry 😅
Player: I was trying to find an angle with you and the birdbath
if Story.white_heart > 0:
	Alice: It's okay.. I didn't mind it too much
Alice: ..and I can keep these too?
Player: Mhmm
Alice: Uhm thanks..
Alice: For showing me
if Story.white_heart > 0:
	Alice: Can I ask you something..?
	Player: Sure
	Alice: Was this a date?..
	- I guess it was [#whiteheart]
		set Story.white_heart += 1
		Player: I guess it was
		Alice: Okay..
		do Story.set_profile_image(\"alice\", \"alice-8\")
	- Not really
		Player: Not really
		Player: Just a photography practice session
		Alice: Oh... I see..
Alice: I have to go now
Player: Bye Alice
Alice: Bye
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
